56.6929133858267775 685.9844881889763428 Td
(Artificial Intelligence \(AI\) is the simulation of human intelligence in machines ) Tj
T* (that are programmed to think and learn. The ideal characteristic of artificial ) Tj
T* (intelligence is its ability to rationalize and take actions that have the best ) Tj
T* (chance of achieving a specific goal.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (There are three main types of AI:) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (1. Artificial Narrow Intelligence \(ANI\): Also known as weak AI, this type of AI ) Tj
T* (   specializes in one area. Examples include virtual assistants like Siri and ) Tj
T* (   Alexa, self-driving cars, and recommendation systems.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (2. Artificial General Intelligence \(AGI\): This is strong AI that can perform any ) Tj
T* (   intellectual task that a human being can do. AGI remains a theoretical concept ) Tj
T* (   and is the goal of many AI research efforts.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (3. Artificial Superintelligence \(ASI\): This would surpass human intelligence and ) Tj
T* (   ability. ASI is currently a hypothetical concept often explored in science ) Tj
T* (   fiction.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Machine Learning is a subset of AI that enables systems to learn and improve ) Tj
T* (from experience without being explicitly programmed. It focuses on developing ) Tj
T* (computer programs that can access data and use it to learn for themselves.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Deep Learning is a subset of machine learning that uses neural networks with ) Tj
T* (multiple layers. These deep neural networks have revolutionized fields like ) Tj
T* (computer vision, speech recognition, and natural language processing.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Neural networks are computing systems inspired by biological neural networks ) Tj
T* (that constitute animal brains. They consist of interconnected nodes called ) Tj
T* (neurons that process information using a connectionist approach to computation.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Natural Language Processing \(NLP\) is the ability of computers to understand, ) Tj
T* (interpret, and generate human language. Applications include sentiment analysis, ) Tj
T* (chatbots, translation services, and text summarization.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (Computer Vision enables computers to derive meaningful information from digital ) Tj
T* (images, videos, and other visual inputs. It powers facial recognition, medical ) Tj
T* (image analysis, and autonomous vehicle navigation.) Tj
T* () Tj
T* (The future of AI includes advancements in explainable AI, federated learning, ) Tj
T* (and edge AI. These technologies will make AI more transparent, privacy-focused, ) Tj
T* (and accessible to everyone.) Tj
ET
